    • Method Detail

      • allowedHealthstates

        default RepositoryInfo.Health[] allowedHealthstates()
        Returns an array of Health statuses in which the delegate request is allowed to execute. By Default the array contains only Repository.Health#GREEN. Which can be overriden in RepositoryRequestBuilder implementations eg.: to allow maintenance related requests to be executed against a non-green Repository.
        Returns:
        an array of Repository.Health statuses.
